                                                     PPC


                This is the seventh release of AmigaVGB PPC!
    It is a recompile with some changes of AmigaVGB (for 68k) on Aminet.
                 Compared with AmigaVGB running on a 060,
       AmigaVGB PPC has a GREAT speed (even faster than a Gameboy!)..


                    @{"              Usage              " Link Usage}

                    @{"             Features            " Link Feat}
                    @{"     Limitations/Requirements    " Link Req}
                    @{"            Known Bugs           " Link Bugs}

